strapiArticle.title: Travelling With Children in Paris
strapiArticle.description: Best Places to take Children in Paris
strapiArticle.content: # Where to take children in Paris - DisneyLand Paris ... Duh! ... [BUY tickets](https://www.disneylandparis.com/en-us/) - Jardin d'Acclimitation Buy tickets/tokens at the front gate - [Google Map](https://g.page/lejardindacclimatation?share) - Jardin du Luxembourg There's a marionnettes theatre in the middle of the park (puppet show). It's in French, just FYI. I enjoyed it but my 5 year old wanted to leave half way through...so we did (not being in English as well as some cultural differences ... my daughter tuned out!) There's a pay-per-access park through some turnstiles right next to the theatre. - Eiffel tower carouselle
